snippet: David Möller of Germany won the men’s singles race at a luge World Cup meet in Königssee, Germany, earning his first victory of the season.
abstract: David Moller of Germany wins the men’s singles race at luge World Cup meet in Konigssee, Germany, earning his first victory of the season.
lead_paragraph: David Möller of Germany won the men’s singles race at a luge World Cup meet in Königssee, Germany, earning his first victory of the season.
